    "body": "The [`currentRefinements`](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/current-refinements/js/) widget in v3 doesn't make the distinction between clearing some and clearing all refinements. It's achieved with the `includedAttributes` and `excludedAttributes` options.\r\n\r\nThis issue is therefore not relevant anymore.",
